    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Temporibus v(enera)b(ilis) et apostolici domni <persName
                            key="#Popes" ref="#people/2410">Benedicto</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">papa</rs> pontific[a]to eius sesto et dies quartus calende
                        aprile, p[er] ind(ici)o(ne) octava, feliciter. Ideo <rs key="#Morgengabe"
                            >cartula de mori[t]incap</rs> quen fazio ego <persName
                            key="#Lombard #marriage"><name ref="Petrus de Iohannes">Petrus filio
                                quondam Ioannis</name></persName> a tibi <persName key="#marriage"
                                ><name ref="Maria de Urso">Maria filia quondam
                            Urso</name></persName> ventura <rs key="#marriage">congnungne</rs> mea,
                        oc est integram quartam pars de omnes movilia et sustanzia mea seo de <rs
                            key="#Gold">aurum</rs> et <rs key="#Metals">arien</rs>, de <rs
                            key="#Horses">cavallis et iumentis</rs>, <rs key="#Cows">de bovis et
                            vahe</rs>, <rs key="#Animals">de domitis et indomitis, de animalia
                            maioris et minoris</rs>, de <rs key="#Metals">eramentis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Iron">fera[m]entis</rs> et <rs>siricamentis</rs> adque
                            <rs>panamentis</rs>, de <rs key="#Gold">iutinsiliis auri</rs> seu de
                        intrinsecus casali, [s]eo de omnia et in onibus movilia et sustanzia mea
                        quecumque modo abeo aut in antea cum Deus adiuvantes aquirere aut parare
                        potuero aut unde cum [aux]ilii ad mea permanerit potestatis aut n[os]
                        pertinere dinusscitur per quamvis modis ingenio; et si ego suprascripto
                        Petrus a tibi suprascripta Maria ventura congnungne mea oc est integram
                        quartam pars moritincap dabo et per uc scripto confirmo abere et ostendo et
                        dabo tibi alia die pos congnungnio nostro quia inter parentis et amicis
                        nostris secundum <rs key="#Lombard">lex mea Langubardorum</rs>, quas
                        benememorio domno et gloriosissimo <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/12">Liuprando</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs> in edicto constituit, qui me manifestu sum
                        abere edicti tinore. Actum loco <placeName>Cernite</placeName>, mense,
                        ind(ici)o(ne) suprascripta; feliciter. Et singno mano de suprascripto Petrus
                        qui in ac cartula de moritincap manum sua scrivere rogavit. Et singno mano
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rainerius">Raineri</name></persName>
                        et singno mano <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Wido"
                            >Guido</name></persName> et singno mano <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Bonitius">Bonizo</name></persName> rogatis <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testis</rs>. Ego Felici not(arius) scripsi et pos tradita conplevi et
                        dedi.</ab>
                </div>
